THOMAS LABS, COMMITTED TO YOUR PET’S HEALTH
Working with veterinarians and animal care specialists Thomas Labs creates unique formulas for pets, companion, and service animals. We source our ingredients from the best suppliers and provide cost effective solutions for both common and hard to treat animal health issues.

“We will not make any product that we would not feel 100% confident using to help our own pets.”

Pets are family, and we have lots of fur, feather and fin family members here at Thomas Labs. We are selfish in the idea that our mission is to help extend the longevity of the animals that share our lives so that we can have extra, quality time with our best friends.
We hope that our natural products will help bring a new awareness to pet owners of what can be accomplished with the use of smart and safe supplements and health specific therapies. Use Thomas Labs health and wellness products for your pets and animals, and trust that we care for your pet’s well-being as much as we care for our own pets and family.

Please contact us with any questions - or call 800-359-8387





